snippet.title: Dosa Podcast | EP 2 - Amber Heard & Horlicks
snippet.description:
In this Podcast, we have our beloved guest Ashutosh Jamadagni . We are going to be talking about Amber Heard and Johnny Depp's controversial case, showing how the media is slightly biased towards both. Then we are going to be critic Taapsee Pannus Horlicks Advertisement, which was very dumb and predict alternative stereotype for the advertisement. Later we going to be talking about how DC/Marvel replacing people with different ethnic background and In the final topic, we are going gonna end it with Ashutosh Favourite Food and his favourite Gwyneth Paltrow Candles. Please watch, like, share and subscribe.
